OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome late
OL,6,Fsunny spells, then clear spells, with
OL,7,Fshowers easing and becoming
OL,8,Fincreasingly confined to coastal
OL,9,Fparts. Touch of frost possible in
OL,10,Fsheltered spots, but breezy near west
OL,11,Fcoast.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FMainly dry start with sunny
OL,14,Fspells but occasionally heavy showers
OL,15,Fdeveloping widely through the morning,
OL,16,Fbefore easing in the west later.
OL,17,FNortherly winds, occasionally strong
OL,18,Fnear coasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
