OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FMainly
OL,6,Fdry with sunny spells through Friday
OL,7,Fand Saturday, risk of overnight
OL,8,Ffrosts. Outbreaks of rain in west
OL,9,FSunday morning edge east before
OL,10,Fclearing from west in afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
